<h1 align="center">
  Tambak Pintar's Disease Map
</h1>

Tambak Pintar is an intensive 3-month program. run by [Jala Tech](https://jala.tech), a startup company that helps shrimp farmers manage their cultivation and create a sustainable farm by using data.

This project is a map dashboard that shows the distribution of shrimp disease in Indonesia. The data was taken by Jala Tech team from the farm that has joined the Tambak Pintar community. The data that were recorded were validated by clinical tests conducted by Jala team.

To learn more details about the Tambak Pintar program, please kindly click the picture below to watch a video about the program.

[![Tambak Pintar Dipasena](https://jala.tech/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/dipasena-e1604581068829.png)](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rFIVZd4EUf0&ab_channel=JALATech)
